    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking for a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride and is still in great shape\u2014really well-cared for and ready to hit the road with its next owner! It drives smoothly and has plenty of life left in it. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know someone else is going to have a blast behind the wheel. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
