    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996-generation Carrera 4S features the 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six, delivering power through a precise 6-speed manual transaxle and a mechanical limited-slip differential. The widebody architecture incorporates Turbo-spec suspension geometry and an all-wheel-drive system for superior lateral grip and high-speed stability. Significant preventative maintenance has been performed, including a ceramic IMS bearing retrofit and a high-flow water pump. The braking system utilizes four-piston monoblock calipers paired with cross-drilled rotors, offering exceptional modulation and heat dissipation. While it displays the expected patina of a well-loved driver\u2019s car, the mechanical integrity remains high, and the throttle response is sharp across the rev range.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Ready for immediate sale.",
