    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between daily utility and pride of ownership. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous finish, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the hood and small surface marks consistent with careful road use. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of cleanliness; the premium upholstery is supple, with only slight softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster, and every button, switch, and climate control function operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is in its prime. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, featuring a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that starts reliably every time. The undercarriage is clean, and the tires offer significant tread life for the seasons ahead. This is an honest, dependable car that has been loved and looked after, ready for its next chapter with a discerning owner.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive engineering, this vehicle represents a superior balance of performance and value. Maintained to exacting standards, it offers a refined driving experience characterized by mechanical reliability and a well-preserved interior. This offering is ideal for the discerning buyer seeking a dependable, high-caliber vehicle that has been thoroughly inspected to ensure it meets our rigorous criteria for roadworthiness and aesthetic appeal.",
