    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the S54 3.2L atmospheric inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system for linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip M Differential Lock, providing exceptional mechanical grip. The chassis has undergone a comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement, addressing common longitudinal stress points for long-term structural integrity. Suspension components remain tight, utilizing a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear arrangement for neutral handling dynamics. Finished in Titanium Silver, the paint is well-preserved with minor stone chips indicative of spirited road use. Recent maintenance includes a shim-and-bucket valve adjustment and a cooling system refresh with a new OE water pump and thermostat.",
